```timing-grid.R
  Obj <- MakeADFun(
    data = Data,
    parameters = Params,
    random = Random,
    checkParameterOrder = TRUE,
    DLL = "covariate_diffusion"
  )
  Obj$env$beSilent()

  times <- list()

<|editable_region_start|>
  out <- system.time({
    Opt <- nlminb(
      start = Obj$par,
      obj = Obj$fn,
      grad = Obj$gr,
      control = list(eval.max = 1e4, iter.max = 1e4, trace = 0)
    )
  })
  times$standard_nlminb <- out[["elapsed"]]

  out <- system.time({
    gr = Obj$gr( Opt$par )
  })
  times$<|user_cursor_is_here|>
<|editable_region_end|>
```
